workflow.name: Capture and schedule HVAC leads with OpenAI, Google Sheets, Slack and SMS
workflow.description:
## Who this workflow is for
Door-to-door HVAC companies seeking automated lead capture and appointment scheduling.

## What this workflow does
AI classifies incoming leads, routes them by service type, logs lead info in Google Sheets, notifies team via Slack, sends confirmations, schedules appointments, and optionally sends SMS reminders.

## How the workflow works
1. Lead submission triggers workflow
2. AI classifies lead
3. Route lead based on service type
4. Log in Google Sheets
5. Notify team via Slack
6. Send confirmation email
7. Schedule appointment in calendar
8. Send SMS reminder (optional)
9. Optional CRM/dispatch integration

**Author:** Hyrum Hurst, AI Automation Engineer  
**Company:** QuarterSmart  
**Contact:** hyrum@quartersmart.com

workflow.name: HVAC Lead Capture and Automated Service Routing

parameters.formDescription: Submit your HVAC service needs and we will get back to you shortly

nodes.name: Classify Lead Urgency and Service Type

options.systemMessage:
You are an HVAC service lead classifier. Analyze the lead information and classify:
1. Urgency level (Low, Medium, High, Emergency)
2. Service category (Installation, Repair, Maintenance)

Consider these factors for urgency:
- Emergency: Words like "not working", "broken", "no heat", "no cooling", extreme temperatures
- High: "soon", "urgent", "ASAP", comfort issues
- Medium: Scheduled maintenance, non-critical repairs
- Low: General inquiries, future planning

Return your classification in the structured format.

Thank You, {{ $json.leadName }}!

We have received your {{ $json.output.serviceCategory }} service request and our team will contact you shortly.

Request Details:

  • Service Type: {{ $json.output.serviceCategory }}
  • Priority: {{ $json.output.urgency }}
  • Address: {{ $json.leadAddress }}

We will reach out to you at {{ $json.leadPhone }} or {{ $json.leadEmail }} to schedule your appointment.

Best regards,
Your HVAC Team

parameters.content:
## Main
Automates door-to-door HVAC lead capture and appointment scheduling. AI classifies leads, routes to appropriate service, logs info, sends confirmations, and schedules appointments.

## Setup
1. Connect Webhook/Form for lead capture
2. Connect OpenAI for lead classification
3. Connect Google Sheets for lead logging
4. Connect Slack for internal notifications
5. Connect email and SMS for client communication
6. Connect calendar for scheduling
7. Optional CRM/dispatch integration

**Author:** Hyrum Hurst, AI Automation Engineer
**Company:** QuarterSmart
**Contact:** hyrum@quartersmart.com
